2019-03-14 20-30-00:
	Title: Playtest 20190825
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: We are thrilled and relieved to finally announce the first public playtest for OpenRA's next release. The playtest brings many new features and improvements:\n\n  • Save/Load support for missions and skirmish\n  • A new spectator/replay interface\n  • A new in-game UI for Tiberian Dawn\n  • Improved order queuing behavior\n  • Direction selection for aircraft-based support powers\n  • Balance changes for RA and TD\n  • Fixes for many bugs and graphical glitches\n\nSee the full news post at www.openra.net for more information and the new playtest download!
